With different varieties of bread.
But what you see may not what you get (see pictures)
Coffee got big and small.
Taking order guy is friendly and polite
Typical local Singapore drink stall. You can get kopi, teh, soft drinks etc here. Kopi C kosong,  kaya butter toast and half boiled eggs combo is a great breakfast in the morning.
Their yuan yang($1.30) is smooth, thick, medium bitterness, has roasted coffee aroma, less sweet and big cup. 8.5/10
Seems to have 2 of the same coffee stall with the same name opposite each other? I went to the older looking one and the coffee was great!
